<listitem><para>Error code from XskZynqMp_Ps_Bbram_ErrorCodes enum if it fails</para></listitem><listitem><para>XST_SUCCESS if programming is done. </para></listitem></itemizedlist>
</para></simplesect>
</para>        </detaileddescription>
